---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { BiLogoPostgresql } from "react-icons/bi";
import { FaDigitalOcean, FaDocker, FaGitAlt, FaGithub, FaPython, FaReact } from "react-icons/fa";
import { SiCss3, SiFastapi, SiRailway, SiRender, SiTypescript } from "react-icons/si";
import { IoLogoJavascript, IoLogoVercel } from "react-icons/io5";
import { RiSupabaseFill, RiTailwindCssFill } from "react-icons/ri";
import { FaLongArrowAltRight } from "react-icons/fa";
import Header from "../../components/landing/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title={"Project RIP QR"}>
  <Header link="/" />
  <div class="bg-[#13151a] text-white md:p-8 space-y-3">
    <div class="px-5">
      <div class="pb-3 md:pb-5 pt-16 md:pt-20">
        <h1
          class="font-bold text-black text-3xl md:text-5xl bg-gradient-to-r rounded-full p-3 text-center from-green-500 to-emerald-400 md:py-4 py-2"
        >
          Project RIP QR
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-wrap text-sm md:text-2xl">
        Service for clients that need to publish about their loved ones, data, videos, photos and
        music. and you can visit the profile of the deceased person scanning the QR code provided by
        the service. This project was made with the purpose of helping people to remember their
        loved ones in a more interactive way.
        <br />
        I used FastAPI for the backend and React for the frontend, and Supabase for the database and
        storage. In addition, I used TailwindCSS for the styles and Digital Ocean for additional Storage.
      </p>
      <div class="w-full mt-4 md:mt-7 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="bg-black p-10 h-fit w-fit justify-center rounded-xl flex flex-col">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-green-500 font-bold md:text-2xl">Key Features</h2>
          <ul
            class="md:ml-10 md:max-w-md max-w-xs ml-5 space-y-3 list-disc mt-2 md:mt-5 w-fit rounded-xl"
          >
            <li class="text-sm md:text-2xl">Focused in local clients</li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-2xl">There are clients using it</li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-2xl">Focus on a memorial view</li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-2xl">part of a physical plate</li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-2xl">
              Admin panel to create profiles and the management of comments
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-between space-y-3 md:space-y-10">
      <div
        class="w-full justify-center items-center flex flex-col to-emerald-400 px-5 text-center md:px-0 py-2 md:py-3"
      >
        <div class="flex rounded-2xl justify-center">
          <div class="flex p-3 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-400 from-green-500">
            <h2 class="text-black lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Admin Panel</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3">
        <div class="w-fit px-6 md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-black p-5">
            <span class="md:text-xl">
              This project works through an admin panel that let us make the management of the
              profiles and comments where you can get the QR Code to share with the client we can
              make the usual operations like read create update and delete. And can upload images to
              the storage and link with an url to the data profile.
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          alt="admin panel"
          src="https://portfolio-raikonif.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/qrmemorias/admin/Screenshot%202024-09-26%20115736.png"
          class="border-y-2 border-green-500 md:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full justify-center items-center flex flex-col to-emerald-400 px-5 text-center md:px-0 py-2 md:py-3"
      >
        <div class="w-fit p-3 px-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-400 from-green-500">
          <h2 class="text-black md:text-black lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Profile Page</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-3">
        <div class="w-full px-6 md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-black p-5">
            <span class="md:text-xl">
              This is the profile page where we found the data of the current person. and let us
              share this profile, as link or QR Code, and we can comment and see the comments of the
              people that visit the profile.
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-end mt-5">
            <a
              href="https://www.qrmemorias.com/profiles/62"
              target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 md:text-2xl text-center hover:underline rounded-xl p-3"
            >
              Profile example <FaLongArrowAltRight />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          alt="profile page"
          src="https://portfolio-raikonif.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/qrmemorias/client/Screenshot%202024-10-16%20162348.png"
          class="border-y-2 border-green-500 md:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="w-full justify-center items-center flex flex-col to-emerald-400 px-5 text-center md:px-0 py-2 md:py-3"
      >
        <div class="w-fit p-3 px-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-400 from-green-500">
          <h2 class="text-black md:text-black lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Landing Page</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-6">
          <div class="bg-black p-5">
            <span class="md:text-xl">
              This is the landing page where we can found all the services option, the steps to get
              a profile and how contact to the owner of this service. In addition you can see a
              guide to use the service and how this works.
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
            <a
              href="https://www.qrmemorias.com/"
              target="_blank"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 md:text-2xl text-center hover:underline rounded-xl p-3"
            >
              Landing page
              <FaLongArrowAltRight />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          alt="landing page
          "
          src="https://portfolio-raikonif.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/qrmemorias/client/Screenshot%202024-10-16%20162957.png"
          class="border-green-500 border-y-2 md:w-1/2"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full justify-center items-center flex flex-col to-emerald-400 px-5 text-center md:px-0 py-2 md:py-3"
      >
        <div class="w-fit p-3 px-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-400 from-green-500">
          <h2 class="text-black md:text-black lg:text-3xl md:text-2xl font-bold">
            Tecnologies Used
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap px-6 gap-3 justify-center">
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-sky-800"
        >
          <FaPython size="25" />
          Python
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-yellow-500"
        >
          <IoLogoJavascript size="25" />
          Javascript
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-blue-600"
        >
          <SiTypescript size="25" />
          Typescript
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-red-500"
        >
          <FaGitAlt size="25" />
          Git
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-blue-700"
        >
          <BiLogoPostgresql size="25" />
          Posgresql
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-cyan-600"
        >
          <FaReact size="25" />
          React
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-green-600"
        >
          <SiFastapi size="25" />
          FastAPI
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-emerald-600"
        >
          <RiTailwindCssFill size="25" />
          TailwindCSS
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-emerald-400"
        >
          <RiSupabaseFill size="25" />
          Supabase
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-blue-900"
        >
          <FaDigitalOcean size="25" />
          Digital Ocean
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-gray-950"
        >
          <FaGithub size="30" />
          Github
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-stone-900"
        >
          <IoLogoVercel size="25" />
          Vercel
        </li>
        <li
          class="flex w-fit gap-3 text-semibold justify-center items-center rounded-full text-xl p-3 bg-slate-900"
        >
          <SiRender size="25" />
          Render
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
